</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/usylokvorak.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sylok Vorak</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>w4nn4b3!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(2/4/02 9:10:35 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumrantsandravesbalancingissues.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1641.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Death of EQ's Casual-Raid Playerbase</span><hr size=1> Hmm casual gamer. Here we go again <br>
